* Twitter social graph script
*  author:kishima
*  mail:kishima7@gmail.com

How to use
 Required modules are as follows,
   rubytter
   ruby-graphviz
 You need to do "gem install module-name"
 
1.Set OAuth parameters
 open libtwitter.rb and modify the initialize method of MyTwitter class.

2.Set Twitter list name and working directory path.
 open checkcomment.rb and makegraph.rb. Then modify @listuser, @listname and @path.

3.Create a member list
 ruby checkcomment.rb checkmembers

4.Check updates
 ruby checkcomment.rb

5.Create a picture
 ruby makegraph.rb > hoge.png
 
